Lemon Tree;;83;;91;;NC;;Set in the West Bank, where Palestinian widow Salma Zidane tends her lemon grove. However, when Israeli Defense Minister Navon moves in across the way, his security guards demand she removes the trees, which could shelter terrorists. Refusing to bow down, she engages lawyer Ziad Daud to take her case to the Supreme Court, which brings international attention.;;Drama;;Eran Riklis;;2009;;Hiam Abbass,Doron Tavory,Ali Suliman,Rona Lipaz-Michael,Tarik Kopty,Amos Lavie,Amnon Wolf,Smadar Jaaron,Danny Leshman,Hili Yalon;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/etz_limon